This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for entity and relation extraction from text. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of knowledge bases and distant supervision, which are common in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques and loss functions, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and databases (cs.DB).
